sectionText: Enrollment Restrictions Notation: No late adds after start of first class without prior written permission of  the professor at bmbarnet@uiuc.edu. No non-degree enrollments. Crosslisted with SOC 420. Restricted to Juniors, Seniors,  and Graduate students with degree status. Not for students with Freshman, Sophomore, Undergraduate Non-Degree, or Graduate Non-Degree class standing.
